element_text:
As the intangible assets are not being traded in an active
and effective market, no residual values after end of use
are included when determining the depreciation period.
Fortjeneste/tab ved salg er medtaget i resultatopgørelsen
under bruttofortjeneste og andre driftsomkostninger.
Profit/loss on sale has been included in the income
statement under gross profit or loss and other operating
expenses.
Materielle anlægsaktiver
Property, plant and equipment
